quran[42]{c,v,t}:
  80,1,"Miyakarimung (so Nabi) go tomiyalikhod,"
  80,2,"Sa Kiyapakatalingoma-on o Bota (a si Abdullah lbno Ommi Maktoum)."
  80,3,"Na antawa-a i kaphakitoka­wan niyan Ruka sa masikun a su­kaniyan na Pushoti,"
  80,4,"O di na Phakindao na ma­kanggai ron a gona so undao?"
  80,5,"Na so tao a Mitharambisa,"
  80,6,"Na Suka na Ayangka gi-i Sha­sagipa-an,"
  80,7,"A kuna a ba Ruka khisundit a di niyan Kapushoti."
  80,8,"Na so puman so miyakaoma Ruka a Mananamar,"
  80,9,"A sukaniyan na Ma-alukun (ko Allah),"
  80,10,"Na Suka na ikaririmorung Ka."
  80,11,"Dingka oto Pupharomani, Mata-an naya! A Pananadum,"
  80,12,"Na sa dun sa khabaya, na Pananadumun niyan."
  80,13,"Matatago ko manga Kitab a Susula-an,"
  80,14,"A ipoporo, a Sosotin,"
  80,15,"A Minggolalan ko manga lima o manga Panonorat,"
  80,16,"A Khisusula-an a Puphaman­gongonotan."
  80,17,"Pimorka-an so Manosiya (a Miyongkir)! Sayana a da-a Tadum iyan!"
  80,18,"Antona-a Shai i pakapo-on niyan, sa Kiya-aduna-on o Allah."
  80,19,"Miyakapo-on sa Notfa Inad­un Niyan go Pindidiyangka lyan,"
  80,20,"Oriyan niyan na so lalan na libod Iyan non,"
  80,21,"Oriyan niyan na ini sabap lyan a kiyapatai niyan, na Piyaki­kobor lyan;"
  80,22,"Oriyan niyan na amai ko kabaya Iyan na Oyagun Niyan mbo."
  80,23,"Sabunar, a da niyan Nggola­lanun so ini Sogo-on (o Allah)."
  80,24,"Na Pamimikirana o Mano­siya so Pangunungkun niyan:"
  80,25,"A Mata-an! A Sukami na inodod Ami so ig sa samporna a kaodod,"
  80,26,"Oriyan niyan na piyakamba­batukad Ami so Lopa sa maroni a kambabatukad,"
  80,27,"Na Piyamakathowan Ami su­kaniyan sa Purpuran,"
  80,28,"Go Anggor, go lulutha-an,"
  80,29,"Go Shaiton, go Qormah,"
  80,30,"Go manga Pamomolan a manga rarabong,"
  80,31,"Go manga Onga, go manga Paotanotan:"
  80,32,"Ka-aniyo kanggonai a go so manga Ayam iyo."
  80,33,"Na amai ko Makatalingoma so lalis,"
  80,34,"Si-i ko Alongan a palagoyan o tao so Pagari niyan,"
  80,35,"Go so Ina iyan, a go so Ama iyan,"
  80,36,"Go so Karoma niyan, go so manga Wata iyan."
  80,37,"Omani isa kiran sa Alongan noto, na adun a butad a Makatu­tumbangon."
  80,38,"Adun a manga Paras sa Alon­gan noto a khisisigai,"
  80,39,"Makakakala, a Mabababaya;"
  80,40,"Go adun a manga paras sa Alongan noto a masasalapot a lopapuk,"
  80,41,"A kakokoloban sa malibo­tung:"
  80,42,"Siran man na siran so Miya­mangongkir a manga baradosa."
